cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.DC, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the comparison of bibliometric databases and their representation of Chinese scientific performance, which falls under the categories of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and computers and society (cs.CY).
